{"tid":1849165,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"突發！哈佛大學化學與生物化學系主任因收受中國巨額資助幫助武漢建立化學實驗室被拘捕！","createTime":"2020-01-29T01:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T01:55:45.000Z","uid":118346,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c66151c8c65f12b9a78421327274ffc3dae47f9e","tid":1849165,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:43:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nbcboston.com/news/local/harvard-professor-charged-federally-with-lying-about-income/2068591/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcboston.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fharvard-professor-charged-federally-with-lying-about-income%2F2068591%2F&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JmFzq3Uwi%2FWN07E9MureYdc%3D&h=9e1dc772\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nbcboston.com/news/local/harvard-professor-charged-federally-with-lying-about-income/2068591/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">A Harvard University professor was charged Tuesday with lying about his ties to a Chinese-run recruitment program and concealing payments he received from the Chinese government for research.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nCharles Lieber, chair of the department of chemistry and chemical biology, is accused of hiding his involvement in China's Thousand Talents Plan, a program designed to lure people with knowledge of foreign technology and intellectual property to China.<br />\n<br />\nLieber was arrested early Tuesday at his office at the Ivy League university, officials said. He remained in federal custody after a brief court appearance Tuesday, pending a detention hearing scheduled for Thursday. A message seeking comment was left Tuesday with his attorney.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Under Lieber's Thousand Talents program contract, prosecutors say, he was paid $50,000 a month by the Wuhan University of Technology in China and living expenses up to $158,000. He was also awarded more than $1.5 million to establish a research lab at the Chinese university, prosecutors said.<br />\n<br />\nIn exchange, prosecutors say, Lieber agreed to publish articles, organize international conferences and apply for patents on behalf of the Chinese university, among other things. </span></strong>"},{"pid":"a8e2790c1f004ffc3df231ea6ff4e54ff8a29180","tid":1849165,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:45:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">隻鬼捉得靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"89b57832e45c892c4d07ed366f4045400eb6be95","tid":1849165,"uid":92347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:46:11.000Z","msg":"咁都查到， 天網灰灰"},{"pid":"c4d1c44afe317a7c1cafc2188afd3cb9c84cbe51","tid":1849165,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f88ad07b48011057237f4f7c32520173e9aabc","tid":1849165,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debc5b25e1b06b07d62dd08ff7d777e48bc84bbd","tid":1849165,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:47:35.000Z","msg":"係咪用反人類罪黎拉鳩佢"},{"pid":"c62560b92c930ba6f0b531e66ae45e3ed8f6f407","tid":1849165,"uid":44562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:48:03.000Z","msg":"又斷咗支那路 , 恭喜恭喜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d3d675abec82972b2ce5002581c0cdeb9ef951","tid":1849165,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T01:48:47.000Z","